Q2: use per-round `context_harness/operator/locks/<round>.events.jsonl`. It keeps lock lifecycle scoped and makes replay easier. Also append a short `process-log.jsonl` event for round-level observability if convenient, but the per-round event log should be authoritative for lock SHA validation.

